{"tid":593350,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Tvb 係咪又燈死人","createTime":"2018-03-15T02:19:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-15T02:20:26.000Z","uid":154004,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0bfd5e3496c8d42fc57be03d3acef9bfd93d8d91","tid":593350,"uid":154004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T02:19:26.000Z","msg":"<strong>近排重播流岷大亨，講緊學仁比人屈殺人（第六集），而做陪審團既do姐(宋楚翹)就指，學仁咁細個，仲係學生無可能徒手扭斷死者條頸。</strong><br />\n<br />\n正當控辯雙方陳詞後，衆陪審員感到表面人證物證俱在，學仁面臨敗訟時，謹昌大爲激動，竟在法庭內理直氣壯爲其弟申辯，終喚起一陪審員宋楚翹的正義感。楚翹經深思熟慮後，發現案件疑點甚多，深信學仁乃無辜，竟主動克服一切阻難，說服其他陪審員繼續研討。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/15/101416_1cc4a967be6d3311e239abbb7442134e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F15%2F101416_1cc4a967be6d3311e239abbb7442134e.png&h=00bbb9f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.orientalsunday.hk/%e5%8a%87%e6%83%85/%e6%b5%81%e6%b0%93%e5%a4%a7%e4%ba%a8-%e5%8a%87%e6%83%85-%e5%85%ad%e8%87%b3%e5%8d%81%e9%9b%86-%e8%90%ac%e6%a2%93%e8%89%af-do%e5%a7%90/2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.orientalsunday.hk%2F%25e5%258a%2587%25e6%2583%2585%2F%25e6%25b5%2581%25e6%25b0%2593%25e5%25a4%25a7%25e4%25ba%25a8-%25e5%258a%2587%25e6%2583%2585-%25e5%2585%25ad%25e8%2587%25b3%25e5%258d%2581%25e9%259b%2586-%25e8%2590%25ac%25e6%25a2%2593%25e8%2589%25af-do%25e5%25a7%2590%2F2%2F&d=IJsfNq5cxxdb7iavmc3bl26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=c16e3914\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.orientalsunday.hk/%e5%8a%87%e6%83%85/%e6%b5%81%e6%b0%93%e5%a4%a7%e4%ba%a8-%e5%8a%87%e6%83%85-%e5%85%ad%e8%87%b3%e5%8d%81%e9%9b%86-%e8%90%ac%e6%a2%93%e8%89%af-do%e5%a7%90/2/</a><br />\n<br />\n潘女遺體其後被舁送台北第二殯儀館，昨午由法醫剖屍檢驗，初步發現死者頸骨有所缺少，鑑證人員昨晨返回棄屍現場檢獲懷疑人骨，其後證實為人體頸椎第一節骨頭，不排除死者遭棄屍後，遺體遭野狗或其他動物咬噬，將部分骨頭叼走。<strong>有消息引述法醫研判，指潘女的頸骨移位，不排除因頸部被扭斷致窒息死亡，惟確實死因仍待進一步檢驗。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180315/mobile/bkn-20180315002031497-0315_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180315%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20180315002031497-0315_00822_001.html&d=IJsfNq5cxxdb7iavmc3bl26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=644a7949\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180315/mobile/bkn-20180315002031497-0315_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"3d10fb7ed1be2587abc868e926de617923c5f559","tid":593350,"uid":113626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T02:20:26.000Z","msg":"txx本身就好邪<br />\n聽講咩有個大佬級人馬係靠D小花輸血比佢<br />\n都係新年聽D親戚講"}]}